WEBVTT

00:00.390 --> 00:02.209
ï»¿The metropolis at the edge of the world...

00:02.293 --> 00:05.437
...is by far one of the most beautiful cities all over the planet.

00:05.905 --> 00:09.633
It's surrounded by amazing golden beaches with white soft sand,...

00:09.973 --> 00:13.751
...craggy mountains with sharp peaks and the best bucolic vineyards.

00:14.212 --> 00:17.647
There are some things and places that you cannot miss while in Cape Town...

00:18.019 --> 00:20.695
...such as the Table Mountain that stands out above the city...

00:20.775 --> 00:21.524
...in the background;...

00:21.913 --> 00:23.263
...the penguins on the beach,...

00:23.498 --> 00:26.433
...the Cape of Good Hope or Chapman's Peak Drive.

00:27.091 --> 00:30.719
Cape Town's climate is on par with California and the Mediterranean...

00:30.980 --> 00:34.491
...with the summer starting in November and lasting until March.

